成年》；12月，他与成龙合作主演动作喜剧电影《铁道飞虎》 。2017年1月，王大陆主演由周杰伦监制的爱情冒险电影《一万公里的约定》；8月，他主演了奇幻电影《鲛珠传》。","name":"王大陆","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"王大陸","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Даррен Ван","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Vương Đại Lục","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"王大陸，1991 年 5 月 29 日出生，台灣男演員。\n\n2008 年，王大陸參演懸疑劇《霹靂 MIT》，以演員身份出道 。2009 年，他出演家庭劇《閃亮的日子》。2010 年，他出演驚悚推理劇《國民英雄》。2015 年，王大陸因在青春校園電影《我的少女時代》中飾演男主角徐太宇而為觀眾熟知，該片成為 2015 年台灣地區年度票房冠軍，在中國內地上映後票房突破 3 億人民幣。2016 年 11 月，王大陸主演愛情電影《28 歲未成年》；12 月，他與成龍合作主演動作喜劇電影《鐵道飛虎》 。2017 年 1 月，王大陸主演由周傑倫監製的愛情冒險電影《一萬公裏的約定》；8 月，他主演了奇幻電影《鮫珠傳》。","name":"王大陸","primary":false}}]}},"person_3607505_translations":{"at":1772647190624,"data":{"id":3607505,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ren Watabe (born 6 March 1999) is a Japanese actor.","name":"Ren Watabe","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"渡部莲","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"渡部蓮","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"רן וואטאבה","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"渡部蓮","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"渡部蓮","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"