b":"Director of Photography"},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2079553,"known_for_department":"Sound","name":"Philippe Brault","original_name":"Philippe Brault","popularity":0.1138,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"697627fdd65382f2c1ab9b9c","department":"Sound","job":"Original Music Composer"}]}},"person_221773_translations":{"at":1772647193764,"data":{"id":221773,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"早見沙織","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"早见沙织（日语：早見 沙織／はやみ さおり Hayami Saori，1991年5月29日—）是日本女性声优、歌手。毕业于早稻田大学，I'm Enterprise所属。东京都出身。身高164cm。\n\n小学4年级的时候知道配音演员的存在，并立志成为配音演员。2004年4月，初中1年级时进入日本播音演技研究所学习。在少年声优班第二年的2006年3月，通过I'm Enterprise的选拔考试。第一次工作是《机械女仆》的Drama CD。之后在2007年透过《桃华月惮》动画出道。幼儿园、小学、初中、高中就读于白百合学园，高中时转入东京都内高中就读。\n\n代表作有《桃华月惮》川壁桃花、《我家有个狐仙大人》蛟、《鹡鸰女神》结、《天降之物》伊卡洛斯、《东之伊甸》森美咲、《爆漫王》亚豆美保、《我的妹妹哪有这么可爱！》新垣绫濑、《只有神知道的世界》白娅·杜·罗德·赫尔梅尼姆、《STAR DRIVER 闪亮的塔科特》扬卷和子、《MM一族》结野岚子、《我们仍未知道那天所看见的花的名字。》鹤见知利子、《机动战士高达AGE》尤琳·路歇尔、《TARI TARI》冲田纱羽、《刀剑神域》幸、《我的青春恋爱物语果然有问题》雪之下雪乃、《请问您今天要来点兔子吗？》青山蓝山、《RDG濒危物种少女》铃原泉水子、《魔法科高中的劣等生》司波深雪、《BUDDY COMPLEX》弓原雏、《众神的恶作剧》草薙结衣、《漫画家与助手》足须沙穗都、《日常系的异能战斗》栉川鸠子、《赤发白雪姬》白雪、《终结的炽天使》柊筱娅、《无彩限的怪灵世界》和泉玲奈、《终末的伊泽塔》菲涅、《风夏》冰无小雪、《宇宙警探élDLIVE》其方美铃、《覆面系NOISE》有栖川仁乃、《BORUTO -火影新世代-》漩涡向日葵、《狂赌之渊》蛇喰梦子、《宝石之国》透绿柱石、《声之形》西宫硝子、《RWBY》Ruby等。","name":"早见沙织","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Saori Hayami is a Japanese voice actress, singer and narrator. She is represented by the agency I'm Enterprise.] As a singer, she is signed to Warner Bros. Home Entertainment Japan. In 2016, she won the 10th Seiyu Awards for Best Supporting Actress.\n\nHer major voice roles include Yukino Yukinoshita in My Teen Romantic Comedy SNAFU, Ayase Aragaki in Oreimo, Shirayuki in Snow White with the Red Hair, Miyuki Shiba in The Irregular at Magic High School, Shinoa Hiiragi in Seraph of the End, Kotohae Hanami in Witchy PreCure!, Urara Shiraishi in Yamada-kun and the Seven Witches, Yotsugi Ononoki in Monogatari, Aila Jyrkiäinen in Gundam Build Fighters, Wako Agemaki in Star Driver, Shōko Nishimiya in A Silent Voice, Yumeko Jabami in Kakegurui – Compulsive Gambler, Shinobu Kocho in Demon Slayer, and Yor Forger en SPY × FAMILY.","name":"Saori Hayami","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Saori Hayami","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"하야미 사오리","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Saori Hayami (早見 沙織, Hayami Saori, nacida el 29 de mayo de 1991) es una actriz de voz (seiyuu), cantante y narradora japonesa de Tokio. Está representada por la agencia I'm Enterprise. Como cantante, tiene contrato con Warner Bros. Home Entertainment Japan. En 2016, ganó el décimo premio Seiyu a la mejor actriz de reparto.\n\nSus principales papeles de voz incluyen Yukino Yukinoshita en Yahari Ore no Seishun Love Comedy wa Machigatteiru., Ayase Aragaki en Ore no Imouto ga Konna ni Kawaii Wake ga Nai, Shirayuki en La Blancanieves pelirroja, Miyuki Shiba en Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei, Shinoa Hiiragi en Seraph of the end, Kotohae Hanami en Maho Girls Precure!, Urara Shiraishi en Yamada-kun to 7-nin no Majo, Yotsugi Ononoki en Monogatari, Aila Jyrkiäinen en Gundam Build Fighters, Wako Agemaki en Star Driver Kagayaki no Takuto, Shōko Nishimiya en A Silent Voice, Yumeko Jabami en Kakegurui, Shinobu Kocho en Kimetsu no Yaiba y Yor Forger en SPY×FAMILY.","name":"Saori Hayami","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"早見沙織是日本的女性聲優、歌手。出身於東京都，所屬公司為 I'm Enterprise。","name":"早見沙織","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","engl